  "texts": [
    "Feature evaluation was done through an in-depth analysis of the functional features of the SIEM systems.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first study that evaluates open-source SIEM solutions based on security and performance features by practically deploying and testing them in a testbed.",
    "Most of the prior work either provides a theoretical comparison of SIEM solutions or evaluates a single SIEM solution in detail.",
    "We conclude that open-source SIEM solutions are essential for SMEs as they provide adequate security while staying within budgetary and resource constraints.",
    "However, not all opensource SIEM solutions provide the same level of security and performance."
  ],
